# Frontend Implementation Guide

## Dashboard Implementation
The main dashboard component is located at [src/components/Dashboard.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/Dashboard.tsx)
- Displays order statistics using React 19 + Vite
- Accessible at http://localhost:5173

## Order Management Components
### Table Component
The order table is implemented in [src/components/OrderTable.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/OrderTable.tsx)
- Displays orders in a table format
- Implements real-time refresh functionality

### Order Creation
New order functionality is split across:
- [src/components/NewOrderButton.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/NewOrderButton.tsx) for the trigger button
- [src/components/NewOrderDialog.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/components/NewOrderDialog.tsx) for the creation form

## API Integration
All API calls are centralized in [src/api/orders.ts](mdc:frontend/src/api/orders.ts)
- Implements CRUD operations
- Handles API responses and errors
- Manages state updates
